      "start": 41.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 96.87999725341797,
      "text": "I'll be standing here, right where you left me, left me I'll be waiting here, right where you left me, left me Cause it makes no sense, all the dark, all the light And it makes no sense that you're in the fight here After all these years, I'll be standing right where you left me",
      "start": 67.77999877929688
    },
    {
