    },
    {
      "end": 150.16000366210938,
      "text": "But right here, where you left me Thinking I'll love something good Thinking I'll love something, something more Than the run of the mill things you throw to the ground So I'm still standing right where you left me",
      "start": 125
    },
    {
      "end": 170.5399932861328,
      "text": "I said I'm still standing right where you left me So if you come back around down the block in your mind And you see me standing there, you'll know I've been here the whole time Here the whole time, don't see your eyes at all",
      "start": 150.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 188.5399932861328,
      "text": "I'm still standing here I'm still standing here, are you? I'm still standing here, are you? I'm still standing here, are you? I'll be standing in my mind",
      "start": 170.5399932861328
    },
    {
